snippet.title: DatzHott - Sean Combs & Trey Songz: Secret Bisexual Love Affairs! EXPOSED?!

localized.description:

Watch the video to learn more about the secret sex lives of your favorite Hollywood celebrities. 

One recording artist who we also learned about while filming this video, is secretly living bisexual lifestyle. You have to watch our series of videos to catch his name. "DatzHott" is an urban digital content provider and news source that gives viewers and readers information about the latest things happening in entertainment, music, and pop culture.

Over the past six years, we've interviewed Hollywood's biggest celebrities, and as well as shot numerous films, music videos, and web series. Our goal  is to provide our subscribers with the opportunity to visit a one stop shop for anything pop culture.
